Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    react.Connection.atPriority(int)
    React originally notified connections lowest priority to highest priority, which was non-intuitive, so it has been reversed and this deprecated method now negates the supplied priority (with special handling for Integer.MIN_VALUE) so as to preserve old behavior for code using the old ordering.
